				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have also used the cammands you are talking about to create emotes for my troll. I made him dance with different emotes. Using the /pause command you can put emotes together so that they follow each other.<BR>
Example:<BR>
/pause 10 /dance<BR>
/pause 5 /shiver say does the Grobb Shuffle<BR>
/cheer say throws his hands in the air<BR>
<BR>
Its been a while since I programmed my hot keys so I may be a little off. But if you play around with it you can make some pretty fun stuff. Trolls are the best dancers in the game by the way. Ogres are a close second )
